title: Emmys 2015: Tracy Morgan Makes Big Stage Comeback - Video
text: In June 2014, comedian Tracy Morgan was involved in a serious car crash, when a trailer operated by a Walmart driver plowed into his own. The impact killed one of the passengers in Morgan’s vehicle and put the star in a coma for over a week.
